  <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg mt-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg text-gray-600">
        Common questions about my Shopify development services
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">How long does it take to develop a Shopify store?</h3>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="faq-icon h-5 w-5 text-primary transform transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content hidden px-5 pb-5 bg-white">
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              The timeline varies depending on the complexity of your project. A basic store customization can take 2-3 weeks, while a fully custom store with complex functionality might take 6-8 weeks. During our initial consultation, I'll provide a more accurate timeline based on your specific requirements.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Do you work with existing Shopify stores or only new ones?</h3>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="faq-icon h-5 w-5 text-primary transform transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content hidden px-5 pb-5 bg-white">
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              I work with both new and existing Shopify stores. Whether you need a brand new store built from scratch or want to improve your current store's design, functionality, or performance, I can help. For existing stores, I'll start with an audit to identify areas for improvement.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">What information do you need to get started?</h3>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="faq-icon h-5 w-5 text-primary transform transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content hidden px-5 pb-5 bg-white">
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              To get started, I'll need information about your business, target audience, product range, design preferences, and any specific functionality requirements. If you have brand guidelines, competitor examples, or websites you admire, those are helpful too. Don't worry if you don't have everything ready – we can work through the details together.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Do you provide ongoing support after the store is launched?</h3>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="faq-icon h-5 w-5 text-primary transform transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content hidden px-5 pb-5 bg-white">
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Yes, I offer ongoing support and maintenance packages to ensure your store continues to run smoothly after launch. This can include regular updates, performance monitoring, bug fixes, and small feature additions. We can discuss support options based on your needs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">How do you handle revisions during the development process?</h3>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="faq-icon h-5 w-5 text-primary transform transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content hidden px-5 pb-5 bg-white">
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Revisions are a natural part of the development process. My project quotes include a specified number of revision rounds at key stages (design, development, pre-launch). I maintain open communication throughout the project, providing regular updates and opportunities for feedback to minimize the need for major revisions later.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-10">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Have more questions about my services?</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-primary hover:bg-secondary focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-primary">
          Contact Me
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
  


